    <entry>
        <base>DESC_FAX_SERVER</base>
        <trans><![CDATA[
	    <p>
            The fax server enables sending and receiving fax using a modem directly connected to the server. <br/> The modem needs to support fax sending and receiving in class 1 or 1.0 (class 2, 2.0 and 2.1 are supported as well).
            </p>
	      ]]> 
        </trans>	
    </entry>

    <entry> 
        <base>DESC_NUM_FAX</base>
