        <trans>Fax Number</trans>
    </entry>
    <entry>
        <base>DESC_LOCAL_ID</base>
        <trans><![CDATA[
            <p>
             Fax sender is usually printed on top (first line) by the receiving fax machine. <br/>
             You can enter a fax number or a name, at most 20 chars long (we recommend using the company name). Use only alphanumeric characters.
            </p>
            ]]></trans>
    </entry>
